<section class="section-main brand-gray-lighter">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12">
                <div class="sidebarBlock richText ">
    <img alt="Willis Chipman Award" src="/~/media/Hatch-Corporate/Homepage/PATHChipman440x310.jpg?h=310&amp;w=440&amp;la=en&amp;hash=95388BCFD81BEBE90B02443A416E58DB481E5AE4" style="height: 310px; width: 440px; float: right; margin: 0px 4px 4px 8px;">
<h3>Hatch wins top prize from Consulting Engineers of Ontario</h3>
<p>Hatch has won the Willis Chipman Award for work on the North West PATH Pedestrian Tunnel in Toronto. We provided both the design and construction management services. The team successfully pushed a tunnel through one of the most utility- and transit-congested intersections in the city of Toronto and delivered the project under budget.</p>
<p>The Willis Chipman Award, the top award given at an awards gala held on April 16th, recognizes projects that have enhanced the quality of life for people living across Ontario and around the globe. </p>
</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
